snippet.title: Quilts and Cats of Calico - Release Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Quilts & Cats of Calico is a wholesome puzzle game full of cats for 1 to 4 players.

WISHLIST THE GAME ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1993180/Quilts_and_Cats_of_Calico/

Meet adorable cats and sew the coziest quilts. Compete with other players in multiplayer mode, play solo, or delve into the story of a quilter sewing their way through the city of cats.
